# Library
```{r}
library(synthpop)
library(labelled)
library(tidyverse)
set.seed(20122021)
```

# Loading Data
```{r}
load("cccu_MA.RData")

load("cccu_R1.RData")

load("cccu_R2.RData")

load("cccu_SA.RData")

load("cccu_R1_s.RData")

load("cccu_R2_s.RData")
```

# Simulate
```{r}
FAKE_cccu_MA = syn(data = cccu_MA)
```


# Save sim data
```{r}
save(FAKE_cccu_MA,
     file = "FAKE_cccu_MA.RData")
```
